<!-- ##### SECTION Title ##### -->
Internationalization

<!-- ##### SECTION Short_Description ##### -->
Internationalization and Localization Support Functions

<!-- ##### SECTION Long_Description ##### -->
<para>
Provides functions and preprocessor macros to aid the application developers
making his software localizable. It also offers functionality similar to the
one introduced in GLib 2.4 and referenced as gi18n. This includes the #Q_
gettext macro and the #xfce_strip_context function.
</para>

<!-- ##### SECTION See_Also ##### -->
<para>
<ulink url="http://developer.gnome.org/doc/API/2.0/glib/glib-I18N.html">GLib
Internationalization</ulink>
</para>

